      type: "Vasopressor (alpha-1 and beta-1 adrenergic agonist)",
      action: "Potent alpha-1 agonist causing arterial and venous vasoconstriction to increase SVR and MAP; mild beta-1 agonism provides modest inotropic support without significant chronotropy; first-line vasopressor for septic shock per Surviving Sepsis Campaign guidelines",
