      sideEffects: "Infusion reactions (fever, chills, rigors, hypotension, bronchospasm -- especially during first infusion), hypogammaglobulinemia with recurrent infections, progressive multifocal leukoencephalopathy (PML -- rare but fatal), hepatitis B reactivation, late-onset neutropenia",
