        options: ["Schedule temporal artery biopsy before starting any treatment","Start prednisone 10 mg daily and recheck ESR in 2 weeks","Administer IV methylprednisolone 1000 mg immediately to prevent permanent vision loss","Order an MRI of the brain to rule out stroke before initiating treatment"],
